div.p:
Republic proclaimed. Government of national defense announced this
                            morning composed of deputies of Paris. Favre, minister of foreign
                            affairs; Gambetta, interior; Picard, finance; Simon, public instruction;
                            Cremieux, justice; Kératry, prefect of police; Arago, prefect of Seine;
                            Glais-Bizon, director of telegraphs; Trochu, governor of Paris and
                            minister of war. Paris quiet. Instruct me.
